# Networking: CTOs from Bitcoin ecosystem businesses will be invited to participate.
# Continue the process of attracting paid developers to enhance BU full-node software on a per-project basis which are approved by technical BUIPs.
# Publicity for BU itself as a growing centre of development excellence for Bitcoin full-node software.
# Intent is to provide high-quality video recordings of the presentations and panel discussions available after the event. Possible live-streaming if deemed suitable.

